title: Oh No! It's the Franciscus Henri video
creator_credit: Trish Foremen, ABC-TV (Australia), Graham Slattery and Rob Pemberton
brief_description: Franciscus Henri has entertained children for many years with his wacky and original songs. After all, a man with a zoo in his house, wearing purple polka-dotted pyjamas, an octopus on his head and who can make unusual pancakes is not to be missed! Stroll with Franciscus Henri through the Milky Way and have lots of fun!
